This token represents a Curve Llama Lend deposit LP. Holders earn interest from users borrowing their supplied crvUSD against the specified collateral, and can also deposit the LP to Curve's gauges to earn CRV emissions. This Llama Lend market accepts WETH as collateral.
Invests the USDS into Sky's Rewards Token Module and auto-compounds the SKY Rewards into more USDS.

This multi-strategy USDC vault allocates to Silo markets on Ethereum that accept LRTs (Liquid Restaking Tokens) and their derivatives as collateral. For more information on the markets either check out the vaults tab or see Silo's [website](https://app.silo.finance).

This token represents a Curve Llama Lend deposit LP. Holders earn interest from users borrowing their supplied crvUSD against the specified collateral, and can also deposit the LP to Curve's gauges to earn CRV emissions. This Llama Lend market accepts [Ethena's](https://ethena.fi/) staked USDe (sUSDe) as collateral.

Supplies {{token}} to multiple [Ajna](https://www.ajna.finance/) isolated lending pools to generate interest.

DISCLAIMER: This Vault deposits into Ajna, a new protocol. The strategies are not 100% liquid. There may be times when you cannot withdraw all of your funds. Proceed with caution.

ALPHA: This vault may also be Juiced with extra rewards. Visit [https://juiced.yearn.fi/](https://juiced.yearn.fi/) to learn more.
